     o Underline
     o Bold
     o Italic
  asl.library V36

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Methods@{ub}

  None defined

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Note@{ub}

  Popstring Open method works with a Popasl object, but Close
  doesn't.

@EndNode

